Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:11.28,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an9\fnTimes New Roman\fs48\b1\bord12\c&H110E10&\3c&HFAF5FD&\blur12\fad(430,1)}SIRIUS's\NYae Niizuma{**-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.59,Default,Shizuka and Kokona,0,0,0,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,"Yae Niizuma, age eleven."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:11.27,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,"A diva for a new generation that \Nappeared out of nowhere at SIRIUS."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.86,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(975,336,768,54)\frz332.6\fnTimes New Roman\fs60\b1\shad3\c&HFAF6F3&\3c&HE0D898&\4c&HCDC57E&}The Little Mermaid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:14.09,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,"She's gained experience from \Na number of performances,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:18.28,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,growing into a performer with talents\N beyond those of a mere child actor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.11,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,They're calling her the \Nnext big SIRIUS star, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:24.37,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,885)\frz329.4\fnArial\fs48\b1\c&HE2C076&\3c&HECECF2&}Future Dai Star {\c&HB06228&}Weekly
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:35.51,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Gosh, if only I could share \Nthe stage with her again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(762.19,501.47)\fscx99.993\fscy97.331\frz47.437\fry-3.364\frx3.41\fax0.303\fnLato\fs24\ybord3.8\c&H211D39&\3c&HF3E9E5&\blur0.5}The results of your second audition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:40.50,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,K-K-Kokona! You've got mail!\N It's from SIRIUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fnArial\fs42\c&H5D5D5D&\3c&HB0C4E5&\4c&HB0C4E5&}The results of your...\N\N{\3c&HF5F5F3&\4c&HF5F5F3&}Kokona Otori{**-sama},\N\NThank you for participating\Nin a second screening. \NAfter careful deliberation,\Nwe'd like to inform you that\N{\fs60}you have passed {\fs42}our audition.\N\N This is your official notification. \N\N Everyone who has passed will be\Ncontacted with further instructions.\N\N We will reach out separately\Nregarding your schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.52,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1029,399)\fnArial\fs96\b1\c&H282241&\3c&HFDFDFD&\4c&HB0C4E5&}you have passed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:48.51,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.54,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,...passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:54.03,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(926.224,101.4)\org(926.199,101.4)\fscx98.651\frz0.684\fry-3.364\fnArial\b1\xbord3.85\c&H4E595B&\3c&HE8EDEC&}Become a World Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:11.58,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.368,413.088)\org(964.368,413.088)\fscy99.662\frx-1.67\fnArial\fs108\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1200,1)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:29.67,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1793.799,920.799)\fnTimes New Roman\fs54\bord3\3c&H4B4B4C&\blur6\fad(770,770)}Copying Someone Else
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:36.59,Subtitles,Kathrina's Subs,0,0,0,,Yes. Everything arrived. Thanks, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:42.59,Subtitles,Kathrina's Subs,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Everything should go okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:44.60,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,333)\fnArial\b1\bord0}SIRIUS SENTO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.86,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Is this really the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.96,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Well, it does say "Sirius."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.98,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Either way, let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.22,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:06.67,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,An otter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.42,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Is it stuffed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:18.30,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,Be nice now, Dugong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.42,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,You must be Kokona{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:26.39,Boxed text,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(478.8,604.002)\fnTimes New Roman\fs48\bord12\c&H7C5A70&\3c&HEBBDE2&\fad(430,1)}SIRIUS President\NSirius Sento Attendant & Matron\NShamo Yamabuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:25.56,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,I'm Yamabuki, the attendant\Nand matron of Sirius Sento.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.75,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,And this little one is Dugong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.54,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Dugong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:34.42,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you!\NI'm Kokona Otori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:39.28,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... This is a bathhouse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:46.87,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,150)\fay0.1\fnArial\fs96\b1\bord12\c&H4536C3&\3c&HDEDDD9&}Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.26,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,Why, yes. Students may use\Nthe baths as much as they'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:46.88,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,In return, you'll help out with the cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.59,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wow, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.75,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,I'll show you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.75,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Great! Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:58.65,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Say, Kokona. She said her name \Nwas Yamabuki, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.94,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Does that mean she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:00.75,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:06.76,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Shamo Yamabuki the World Dai Star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:11.08,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,You're going to make me blush,\Nreacting like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:20.55,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,I happened to see your performance\N during your audition, Kokona{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.81,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:26.56,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,I found it quite mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:30.08,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I, uh, ended up panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:34.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm honestly not sure how I passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.71,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.15,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,Then I guess you'll have \Nto find yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:41.45,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Find myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.74,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,This is your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.60,Subtitles,Kathrina subs,0,0,0,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Kathrina{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.12,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.37,Default,Shamo,0,0,0,,Make sure you two get along from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.50,Default,Kokona; Kathrina; Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:16.62,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'd like to officially welcome you to SIRIUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.86,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I request my own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.14,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I can't sleep unless I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:25.13,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's part of a troupe's job to ensure\Nits talent is taken care of, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:28.77,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,On the stage, you may end up playing \Nfamily members or lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It's probably not a bad idea \Nto get to know one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.39,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,We may also end up playing mortal enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:39.53,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,And hopefully you'll be able to find\Nsomething to inspire that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um, Kathrina{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.10,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm totally okay with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.06,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I promise I don't toss and turn much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:50.06,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't snore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.53,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You do talk in your sleep, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.65,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I m-might talk in my sleep a bit, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.60,Subtitles,Kathrina Subs,0,0,0,,Just be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.90,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:03.71,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,All right, fine. I came all \Nthis way to become a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.80,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I suppose I can deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,A Dai Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.00,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,So, when's our next show? \NWhat role will I be playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.02,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You hope to take the stage so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.11,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,O-Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.39,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What role will I be playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.52,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,At SIRIUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.29,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,anytime a new member joins,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:27.61,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,we give them a single debut\N performance during a production.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.28,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(954,504)\fnTimes New Roman\fs48\bord0\c&H325E2E&}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.27,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:36.29,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The two of you will audition\Nfor the lead role of Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:37.68,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The lead role?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I get to play the lead role?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.28,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Did you miss the "audition" part?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.24,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i0} be taking the lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.67,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Whoever fails to get the role
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:51.01,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,will be playing the lady-in-waiting\Nwho serves Princess Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We'll hold the audition in a week, \Nthe day before dress rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.16,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Don't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.21,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,My first script!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:11.34,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I wonder if Yae{**-chan}'s playing \NPrincess Kaguya in the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.51,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan} as Princess Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.15,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,So good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.96,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,She could ask me to do anything!\NEven the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey, could you quit talking to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:22.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,O-Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.27,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Won't this make it harder to chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.85,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,And what's up with all the luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.47,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,It's really cramped over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:36.42,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hey, you want to be a Dai Star too, right?{sgt: removed "Kathrina-chan" to avoid awful linebreak that was doubly worse with the honorific removed}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.61,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Is your goal to be a World Dai Star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.34,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,That's, like, every actor's goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.37,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'll give you some great life advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.55,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You can't see the forest for the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.60,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,A wannabe actor like you talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.86,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,being a Dai Star,\Nlet alone a World Dai Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.86,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you consider that \Nrather presumptuous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:08:01.44,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Dai Stars can fill theaters all by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.83,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You can't become one simply\Nbecause you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.30,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Only the chosen few make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.00,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,And you're not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:12.27,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,You and I are competing for roles.\NWe're not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Don't bother me more than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.69,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:25.81,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,People call me Panda{**-chan}, \Nthe cutest girl at SIRIUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.05,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Want to have a bath time party with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.89,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Yikes, what the heck did I walk into?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.70,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,150)\fnArial\fs96\b1\bord12\c&H4536C3&\3c&HF1F1F1&}Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.25,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Hey, can I call you Koko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:48.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? U-Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.67,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:54.12,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{*}I like nicknames since they're not so stiff.{*Using "-san" is just so stiff.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.45,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Also, no need to be formal with us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.00,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We're younger than you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.79,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Right, Sassu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:03.93,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The only things that should be stiff \Nare concrete and nata de coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:07.81,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh? Nata de coco?\NWait, is it even that stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.83,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Now I want some nata de coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:14.76,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,You don't need to take the\N things Sassu says too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.11,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Thinking about them too hard \Nis just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.59,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Ah, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:30.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(561,153,375,153)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H589CAE&\3c&H76E6EB&}Panda
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:30.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(882,339,711,339)\fnArial\fs42\c&H589CAE&\3c&H76E6EB&}Chisa Sasuga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:30.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(1482,816,1302,816)\fnGeorgia\fs54\c&H589CAE&\3c&H76E6EB&}Kokona Otori
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.91,0:09:23.84,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Now, why are things so insanely \Ntense with you and Kathrin?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.23,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm not sure tense is the right word...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.86,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I think she just dislikes \Nme for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:36.47,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'd like to be her friend,\Nbut I guess she feels differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.97,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,She said we're competing for roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:43.98,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I mean, she does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:50.48,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(423,789)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H589CAE&\3c&H76E6EB&}Panda
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:50.48,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1644,789)\fnArial\fs42\c&H589CAE&\3c&H76E6EB&}Chisa Sasuga
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.61,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,No matter how close you are,\Nif you're striving to become Dai Stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:49.98,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,you're going to butt heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.91,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean you \Ncan't understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.18,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We're all actors, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.09,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.11,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.63,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,First, I'll make her acknowledge\Nme as an actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:08.29,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,To that end, I'll do my best\Nfor the Kaguya audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.88,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,141)\fnGeorgia\fs54\bord0\c&HC9CAC9&}Kokona Otori
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.88,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1086,114)\fnArial\fs54\bord0\c&HC9CAC9&}Kathrina Griebel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(679.668,159.333,551.667,153.333)\fay0.2\fnArial\fs54\b1\c&H3A3F7A&\3c&H71669D&}Coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(1520.337,362.001,1386.336,362.001)\fay-0.27\fnTimes New Roman\fs54\b1\c&H3285CB&\3c&H141D38&}Royal Coffee Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(1679.67,940.668,1554.336,940.668)\fay-0.22\fnTimes New Roman\fs36\c&H121827&\3c&H67B8E0&}Roasted In Store
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.93,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NI haven't seen Yae{**-chan} at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.74,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Niizumacchi said she'd \Nbe camping for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:54.77,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.368,386.907)\org(964.368,386.907)\fscy99.662\frx-1.67\fnArial\fs108\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1200,1)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.86,Default,Sasuga Fan A,0,0,0,,What's Chisa{**-san} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.49,Default,Sasuga Fan B,0,0,0,,Don't disturb her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.78,Default,Sasuga Fan B,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's waiting for \Nher role to descend upon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:32.43,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Man, the sun is bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.12,Default,Sasuga Fan B,0,0,0,,She speaks the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.63,Default,Sasuga Fan A,0,0,0,,Well said, Chisa{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.75,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Sassu, rehearsal is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.59,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I told you to stop basking in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:48.65,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I-I'm Kokona Otori! Thank you for \Nhelping me out at the audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.52,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I love you! I can't wait to work with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.42,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You should've kept some of that to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.61,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Also, what's with the hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.64,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Ah, that's not what I meant by love!\NYae{**-chan}, er, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:00.94,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Niizuma{**-san}, your acting is just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.81,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,You can call me Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:06.52,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for not properly \Nintroducing myself before now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.82,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.67,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.03,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yae, we're going to begin rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:14.84,Default,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.21,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(959.334,594.666)\frz330.3\fnTimes New Roman\bord0\c&H325E2E&}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.71,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,All right, begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:32.33,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,She will be here to serve your every \Nneed starting today, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:38.47,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to meet you.\NMy name is Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.86,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Misao{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:41.88,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:47.91,Default,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,I thought you'd be more comfortable \Nwith a girl close to your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.60,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Misao{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.99,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:57.63,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Misao{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.95,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,C-Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:01.76,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.57,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.52,Overlap,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,{\an8}Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:06.02,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}'s so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.10,Overlap,Sasuga (Old Man),0,0,0,,{\an8}Princess, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:11.03,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the story of the ill-fated\NPrincess Kaguya, who was born of bamboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:13.46,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Japan's oldest sci-fi story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:19.41,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the play, Kaguya and her attendant Misao\N grow up like sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:22.86,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}and dread the day they \Nwill eventually have to part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:26.37,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's SIRIUS's take on\N{\i0}The Tale of the Bamboo Cutter{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.13,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Next up is the audition scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:30.91,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:38.27,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Hey, have you ever seen \Na bamboo blossom, Misao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.31,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,A bamboo blossom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:46.33,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,The books say they bloom \Nonly once every 120 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.88,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,Once every 120 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:56.05,Default,Niizuma (Kaguya),0,0,0,,I hope we can see one together someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,How pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:30.62,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Her singing voice sounds so sweet,\Nbut I feel sad for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:35.18,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,This is a far more mature performance\Nthan the innocent act she had at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.55,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The song conveys her emotional turmoil \Nand sorrow over the impending goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:43.93,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Just listening to it makes \Nus feel her pain as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:53.43,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan} really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:15:00.54,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can perform like that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1483.739,884.001)\org(1479.999,884.001)\fscx97.661\fscy87.553\frz-217.167\fry3.364\frx11.922\fax-0.106\fnTimes New Roman\fs36\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H212034&}Princess Kaguya\N Manju
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:10.22,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Man, starting off with {\i1}The Bamboo Cutter{\i0}?\NHiiragi{**-san}'s a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.14,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,It's interesting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.89,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,If it were any normal play,\Nit easily would've been Kathrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:19.03,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Well, Japanese culture {\i1}is{\i0} pretty unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:22.60,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,For Kathrin, even the act of holding a tea cup
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.93,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,may come off as mannered and\N make the performance unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:30.15,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,She can fool us with her line reads,\Nbut not with her mannerisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:34.49,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Having to become thoroughly\NJapanese inside of a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.28,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Pretty tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:41.04,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Koko{**-chan} honestly lacks skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:45.46,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I wonder if what we saw\Nat her audition was a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:51.30,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Personally, I'm wondering why Hiiragi{**-san} \Noverruled all objections and passed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.60,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It's a little mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.78,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The key to victory is what lies within them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.93,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Their Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:03.34,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,By the way, Sassu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.60,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,There isn't a whole box\Nfor each of us, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:08.86,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(480.739,297.333)\org(480,297.333)\fscx91.125\fscy99.876\frz2.411\fry-9.234\frx0.732\fax-0.023\fnTimes New Roman\fs36\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H212034&}Princess Kaguya\N Manju
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.87,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.52,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,How was my performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.31,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Well, it was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:21.79,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But if you're asking if it's enough \Nto beat Kathrina... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:25.72,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah... This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:28.41,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I wonder what Kaguya's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:32.05,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, but the lady-in-waiting \Nrole is pretty nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.69,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.62,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You need to go for the lead role \Nif you want to be a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.26,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:43.60,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You were totally different\Nat the SIRIUS audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.68,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Your whole demeanor, enthusiasm... \NI can't put it into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.27,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,If you can do that again, \Nyou might be able to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:53.88,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You mean act like I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.82,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Tell me, Kokona.\NHow did you embody the prince then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.78,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:06.93,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan} asked me what kind \Nof performer I wanted to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:11.59,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,so I tried to imagine how \Nyou'd play the role, Shizuka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.42,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:17.58,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh... So you want to be like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:22.28,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you try\Ndoing the same thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:22.84,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.11,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We'll plan out how to play the part,\Nand you'll see it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.86,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,The both of us will play the role!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.38,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,The both of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.83,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,How would you perform \Nthis scene, Shizuka{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:38.96,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.87,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.88,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:17:59.88,Overlap,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.21,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Ooh, so fresh and new!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:07.83,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Kokona came to watch every rehearsal,\Nbut Kathrina didn't come to a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.28,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,We barely even saw her at the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.61,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,I wonder how she's going to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We'll start with Kathrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:18.33,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Panda, run the scene with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:20.21,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.29,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see what she's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:28.78,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Japanese people point to themselves,\Nthey point at their noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.59,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}We put our hands to our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.05,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the most trivial differences can \Nmake a performance seem unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.88,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure they think that, \Nbecause I haven't been in Japan long,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:43.87,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm incapable of expressing\N Kaguya's inner life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.22,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}They can think whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.45,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,All right, begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.84,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Hey, have you ever seen \Na bamboo blossom, Misao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:00.72,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,A bamboo blossom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:07.42,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,The books say they bloom \Nonly once every 120 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.73,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,Once every 120 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:14.77,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh... Not bad. She's moving like \Nsomeone who's worn a kimono before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.58,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Just lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.33,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.50,Default,Kathrina (Kaguya),0,0,0,,we can see one together someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.94,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1354.665,555.999)\frz286.7\fnTimes New Roman\fs36\c&H858B8E&\3c&HFEFFFD&\4c&H695FB1&\fad(560,110)}How to Beautifully Wear\Nand Move in a Kimono
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.84,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been one week since \NI received this script.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.47,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's 168 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:34.31,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,{\i1}More time than I'd ever need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:47.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wow... She's even better than \Nshe was in {\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.09,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}She feels no emotion \Nwhatsoever towards her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.23,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet she can still pull it off
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.96,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}because she studied countless sources
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.88,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and acquired the movements necessary \Nto play Kaguya from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:04.83,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The focus required to pull this together\Nin what little time she had
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:08.03,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Kathrina's Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.23,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your enemy cleared\Nher hurdle with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.79,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you gonna do, Koko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.66,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Next, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:45.01,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.93,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,It's okay. You've got this, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}The both of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.54,Default,Kokona (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:06.21,Default,Kokona (Kaguya),0,0,0,,Have you ever seen a bamboo blossom, Misao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.70,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh... This is different from \Nwhat I saw in rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.78,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,A bamboo blossom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:19.53,Default,Kokona (Kaguya),0,0,0,,The books say they bloom \Nonly once every 120 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.31,Default,Panda (Misao),0,0,0,,Once every 120 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:27.30,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's playing a Kaguya who's trying \Nto be cheerful to hide her loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.57,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this strategy Shizuka{**-chan} planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.47,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.38,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:01.02,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.70,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niizumacchi's performance.
